Hero MotoCorp Ltd. (HMCL), on Wednesday, forayed into the world of motorcycle rally by forming a strategic partnership with Speedbrain GmbH, the German off-road racing specialist.
India’s C.S.
Santosh and Joaquim Rodrigues of Portugal will be part of the newly formed ‘Hero MotoSports Team Rally’.
